  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK924">
<l>nāṇeṉṉu nallāḷ puṟamkoṭukkuṅ kaḷḷeṉṉum </l>
<l> pēṇāp peruṅkuṟṟat tārkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The fair maid of modesty will turn her back on those who are guilty of the great and abominable crime of drunkenness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
